    • Enum Constant Detail

      • NONE

        public static final MesosEventClient.ClientStatusResponse.IdleRequest NONE
        The client has no requested actions for upstream to perform.

      • START_UNINSTALL

        public static final MesosEventClient.ClientStatusResponse.IdleRequest START_UNINSTALL
        The client has finished running and should be switched to uninstall mode by the caller. This is used for services which run once and then exit, and is only applicable to multi-service mode.

      • REMOVE_CLIENT

        public static final MesosEventClient.ClientStatusResponse.IdleRequest REMOVE_CLIENT
        The client has finished its uninstall. In multi-service mode, this means that the service can be removed from the parent scheduler. When uninstalling the scheduler itself, this means that the scheduler can be torn down, assuming that all other services have also reached UNINSTALLED.
